          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "LiF of natural isotopic content. Targets consisting of",
                " 0.025 mg/cm2 LiF, evaporated on to thin carbon foils,",
                "approximately 0.0135 mg/cm2 in thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "This experiment was secondary to that of 19F(d,p)20F",
                " (see REL-REF). Two methods have been used to estimate",
                "the absolute differential cross sections for the",
                "lithium groups, since the absolute beam-charge incident",
                "on the target could not be reliably measured.",
                " 1. Results obtained by Ono et al. (see MONIT-REF) were",
                "used to determine  the constant of proportionality (K)",
                "taking into account that the angular distributions",
                "obtained by these authors and present results are",
                "closely similar.",
                " 2. The second method for obtaining K uses the measured",
                "absolute cross section of the 12C(d,p0)12C reaction",
                " (see REL-REF) and the ratio of the number of 6Li to",
                "12C atoms in the target."
              ]
            }
          ],
